              <span id="reviewTextContainer1946452812" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4792551878666778879">Shrieking, hard, irritating, and intimidating, fit only for belief revision, here is the work as an invitation for reconsideration, not merely a novel. Life is Elsewhere dislocates its readers and gets us out of the comfort zone, bringing us face to face with our worst fears. What if our lives did not really matter and what if our emotions were merely pathetic!<br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


